      "side": 1,
      "message": "minor: I don\u0027t grasp why `rs.Run.Submission.GetLastTreeCheckTime()` check is needed.\n\nIF defensive programming, then i think it should be \"... \u003d\u003d nil || ...\" meaning \"either never checked OR \u003e\u003d1 minute old).\n\nELSE, I think `!rs.Run.Submission.GetTreeOpen()` means that tree was checked, and hence the time must be set.\n\nHave I missed something?",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 50,
        "startChar": 43,
        "endLine": 50,
        "endChar": 52
      },
      "revId": "9f3ca92791d82a87f69ae9c6855eecb29da9066e",
